rows.label: tlk43700143_03_msg0001
rows.name:
It's risky business, being
a merc. You never know when
your time'll be up.

rows.label: tlk43700143_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I keep having to remind
myself that every time I'm
heading out on a mission.

rows.label: tlk43700143_03_msg0003
rows.name:
What happened on Temperantia,
though...now that was a disaster.

rows.label: tlk43700143_03_msg0004
rows.name:
My thoughts go out to those poor
souls who lost their lives there.

rows.label: tlk43700143_03_msg0005
rows.name:
They were wiped out by something out
of their control. No amount of skill
or preparation could have helped them.

rows.label: tlk43700143_03_msg0006
rows.name:
The ones who made it out alive
just had the better luck.

rows.label: tlk43700143_03_msg0007
rows.name:
If lives are lost and wars are won
through chance, we may as well decide
them with Gladiator Wrestling...

rows.label: tlk43700143_03_msg0008
rows.name:
It's a game where you get little paper
dolls and nudge them with your finger
to try and knock your opponent over.

rows.label: tlk43700143_03_msg0009
rows.name:
They're selling sets at Hobby
Knick-Knacks if you're interested.
